{
  "text": "Thank you. Is there anything we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or improve the contact? This instrument is well balanced and the contact is as it should be. This instrument has certain difficulties of a distortion you would call the muscular spasm, thus making the motionless position on comfortable. Thus we leave the instrument. I am Ra. You are doing well, my friends. I leave you in the love and the light of the one infinite Creator. Go forth then, rejoicing in the power and the peace of the one creator Adena. Okay.",
